     rdfs:comment "Potential of the working electrode against a reference electrode, in volt. Vendor-only. Note the Arbin unit-label bug 'Reference_Voltage(Ohm)' (labelled ohm but carrying volts). In some h5 exports the equivalent channel appears as an auxiliary voltage."@en .

